text: Steamboat Rock can refer to some places in the United States: * Steamboat Rock, Iowa, a town in Iowa ** Steamboat Rock Consolidated Schools Building * Steamboat Rock (Garden of the Gods), a rock in Colorado Springs * Steamboat Rock (Colorado), a large rock at the confluence of the Green River (Colorado River) and Yampa River in the state of Colorado * Steamboat Rock State Park in the state of Washington
title: Steamboat Rock
